property_value: IAO:0000602 "(forall (x) (if (ThreeDimensionalSpatialRegion x) (SpatialRegion x))) // axiom label in BFO2 CLIF: [040-001] " xsd:string {IAO:0010000="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/040-001"}
