disjoint_from: OGMS:0000045 ! disorder
property_value: editor_note "10/21/09: This is a placeholder term, that should ideally be imported from the NCBI taxonomy, but the high level hierarchy there does not suit our needs (includes plasmids and 'other organisms')" xsd:string
property_value: editor_note "13-02-2009:\nOBI doesn't take position as to  when an organism starts or ends being an organism - e.g. sperm, foetus.\nThis issue is outside the scope of OBI." xsd:string
