property_value: editor_note "Titus Schleyer 3/13/2014: updated definition\n\nBill D. 08-04-2023: Not all resins are tooth colored. Some are cream colored. Also, updated definition source Craig's restorative Dental Material." xsd:string

[Term]
id: OHD:0000037
name: direct dental material insertion process
def: "A material combination in which a moldable restorative material is placed directly into or on the tooth. The material then hardens and becomes (essentially) part of the tooth. " []
is_a: OBI:0000652 ! material combination
relationship: OBI:0000293 UBERON:0001091 ! has_specified_input calcareous tooth
property_value: editor_note "Bill Duncan 12/11/2014:\nMoved from this class from being a subtype of tooth restoration procedure to being a subclass of material combination." xsd:string
property_value: editor_note "Titus Schleyer 1/1/2014: made definition clearer" xsd:string
property_value: IAO:0000117 "Bill Duncan" xsd:string

[Term]
id: OHD:0000038
name: dental material tooth attachment process
def: "A material combination in which a rigid piece of restoration material is attached to a tooth. The restoration is attached to the tooth by mechanical forces or some form of cement or glue. " []
is_a: OBI:0000652 ! material combination
relationship: OBI:0000293 UBERON:0001091 ! has_specified_input calcareous tooth
property_value: editor_note "Bill Duncan 12/11/2014:\nMoved from this class from being a subtype of tooth restoration procedure to being a subclass of material combination." xsd:string
property_value: editor_note "Bill Duncan 12/16/2014:\nUpdated definition.\n\nOriginal definition:\nA material combination in which a rigid restoration, such as a gold inlay, is attached to a tooth. The restoration is attached to the tooth by some form of cement or glue. \n\n1. Removed \"such as a gold inlay\".\n\n2. Added that the material may be held in place by mechanical forces" xsd:string
property_value: editor_note "Titus Schleyer 1/14/2014: made the definition consistent with that of direct restoration" xsd:string
property_value: IAO:0000117 "Bill Duncan" xsd:string

