[Term]
id: OHD:0001008
name: calcium aluminate glass ionomer hybrid cement dental restoration material
def: "A dental restoration material containing calcium aluminate, polyacrylic acid  with basic ion-leachable glass particles as powder component with water as liquid component to complete the acid-base reaction of glass ionomer and hydration of calcium aluminate cement." []
is_a: OHD:0000000 ! dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-02-08T11:22:23Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001010
name: zinc oxide non-eugenol cement dental restoration material
def: "A zinc-oxide cement dental restoration material containing aliphatic acid or butyric acid to substitute the eugenol as a liquid component to complete the acid-base reaction." [] {IAO:0000119="ISBN:0323478212", IAO:0000119="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC9689175/"}
is_a: OHD:0001022 ! zinc oxide cement dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-07-31T12:05:19Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001011
name: bulk-filled resin-based composite dental restoration material
def: "A resin-based composite dental restoration material that enables the restoration to be built up in thick layers of up to 4 mm and are recommended by manufacturers to simplify clinical technique and save time compared to traditional incremental placement." [] {IAO:0000119="Craig's restorative Dental Material"}
is_a: OHD:0000036 ! resin-based composite dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-07-31T12:07:09Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001012
name: flowable resin-based composite dental restoration material
def: "A resin-based composite dental restoration material that has low-viscosity and is recommended for cervical lesions, restorations in deciduous teeth, and other small, low- or non-stress bearing restorations." [] {IAO:0000119="Craig's restorative Dental Material"}
is_a: OHD:0000036 ! resin-based composite dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-07-31T12:07:24Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001014
name: macrofilled resin-based composite dental restoration material
def: "A resin-based composite dental restoration material that contains macrosize filler particles." [] {IAO:0000119="Craig's restorative Dental Material"}
is_a: OHD:0000036 ! resin-based composite dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-07-31T12:08:04Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001015
name: microfilled resin-based composite dental restoration material
def: "A resin-based composite dental restoration material which is composed of dimethacrylate resins with 0.04-m colloidal silica fillers and prepolymerized resins, which are sometimes filled with colloidal silica." [] {IAO:0000119="Craig's restorative Dental Material"}
is_a: OHD:0000036 ! resin-based composite dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-07-31T12:08:13Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001017
name: nano filled resin-based composite dental restoration material
def: "A resin-based composite dental restoration material that contains nanometer-sized filler particles (1 to 100 nm) throughout the resin matrix." [] {IAO:0000119="Craig's restorative Dental Material"}
is_a: OHD:0000036 ! resin-based composite dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-07-31T12:08:41Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001018
name: nano hybrid resin-based composite dental restoration material
def: "A resin-based composite dental restoration material which consist of large particles \n(0.4 to 5 m) with added nanometer-sized filler particles. Thus they are hybrid materials, not true nanofilled composites." [] {IAO:0000119="Craig's restorative Dental Material"}
is_a: OHD:0000036 ! resin-based composite dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2023-07-31T12:08:57Z" xsd:dateTime
