[Term]
id: OHD:0001019
name: compomer resin-based composite dental restoration material
def: "A resin-based composite dental restoration material that contains fluoride-releasing silicate glass filler phase and a methacrylate based matrix with carboxylic acid functional groups." [] {IAO:0000119="Craig's restorative Dental Material", IAO:0000119="ISBN: 978-1-4377-2418-9"}
xref: ISBN: 978-81-312-3488-4
