[Term]
id: OHD:0001022
name: zinc oxide cement dental restoration material
def: "An acid-base cement dental restoration material containing zinc-oxide as a powder component with some specific liquid component to complete the acid-base reaction." []
is_a: OHD:0001021 ! acid-base cement dental restoration material
