[Term]
id: OHD:0001045
name: calcium hydroxide cement dental restoration material
def: "A dental restoration material that contains calcium hydroxide as a chief ingredient and is suspended in a solvent carrier with a thickening agent." []
is_a: OHD:0000000 ! dental restoration material
relationship: has_part CHEBI:31341 ! calcium dihydroxide
