[Term]
id: OHD:0001046
name: alumina toughened zirconia ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A polycrystalline composite ceramic dental restoration material that combine alumina to increase materials strength and toughness." []
is_a: OHD:0001040 ! polycrystalline composite ceramic dental restoration material
relationship: has_part CHEBI:30187 ! aluminium oxide
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:45:12Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001047
name: resin matrix ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A ceramic dental restoration material that consists of a ceramic network infiltrated with a polymer resin to integrate the mechanical properties of ceramics with the improved elasticity of resins." []
is_a: OHD:0000135 ! ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:45:40Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001048
name: resin nano ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A resin matrix ceramic dental restoration material that contains nano ceramic filler, typically to improve esthetics, strength, and wear resistance." []
is_a: OHD:0001047 ! resin matrix ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:46:29Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001049
name: resin matrix glass ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A resin matrix ceramic dental restoration material that contains either lithium disilicate or leucite-reinforced glass ceramic filler, typically to improve esthetics, strength, and wear resistance." []
is_a: OHD:0001047 ! resin matrix ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:46:51Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001050
name: resin matrix zirconia silica ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A resin matrix ceramic dental restoration material that contains zirconia or silica based ceramic filler, typically to improve esthetics, strength, and wear resistance." []
is_a: OHD:0001047 ! resin matrix ceramic dental restoration material
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:47:07Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001051
name: feldspathic glass matrix ceramic dental restoration material
def: "A glass matrix ceramic dental restoration material that primarily contains a ternary material system composed of kaolin (hydrated aluminosilicate), silica, and naturally occurring feldspar (a mixture of potassium and sodium aluminosilicates)." []
is_a: OHD:0001032 ! glass matrix ceramic dental restoration material
relationship: has_part CHEBI:140503 ! kaolin
relationship: has_part CHEBI:48733 ! feldspar
relationship: has_part ENVO:01000481 ! silica-based glass
