def: "A synthetic glass matrix ceramic that contains a lithium disilicate system (SiO2-Li2O-K2O-ZnO-P2O5 Al2O3-[zirconium dioxide] ZrO2)." []
is_a: OHD:0001052 ! synthetic glass matrix ceramic dental restoration material
relationship: has_part OHD:0001081 ! lithium oxide
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6424-4096
property_value: dcterms:created "2024-08-30T13:48:33Z" xsd:dateTime

[Term]
id: OHD:0001055
name: fluorapatite based synthetic glass matrix ceramic dental restoration material
