id: OHD:0010246
name: trigeminal neuralgia due to multiple sclerosis
def: "Trigeminal neuralgia caused by a multiple sclerosis (MS) plaque or plaques in the pons or trigeminal root entry zone, and associated with other symptoms and/or clinical or laboratory findings of MS." []
