[Term]
id: OHD:0010285
name: persistent idiopathic dentoalveolar pain without somatosensory changes
def: "Persistent unilateral intraoral dentoalveolar pain, rarely occurring in multiple sites, with variable features, recurring daily for more than 2 hours per day for more than 3 months, unaccompanied by somatosensory changes and in the absence of any preceding causative event." []
