[Term]
id: OHD:0010286
name: persistent idiopathic dentoalveolar pain with somatosensory changes
def: "Persistent unilateral intraoral dentoalveolar pain, rarely occurring in multiple sites, with variable features, recurring daily for more than 2 hours per day for more than 3 months and accompanied by negative and/or positive somatosensory changes, in the absence of any preceding causative event." []
