synonym: "mucous membrane" EXACT [FMA:85355]
synonym: "organ mucosa" EXACT [FMA:85355]
synonym: "region of mucosa" RELATED [FMA:85358]
synonym: "tunica mucosa" RELATED OMO:0003011 [BTO:0000886, Wikipedia:Mucous_membrane]
