[Term]
id: UBERON:0003655
name: molar tooth
def: "Molars are the rearmost and most complicated kind of tooth in most mammals." [https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/221, Wikipedia:Molar_(tooth)]
subset: human_subset
subset: mouse_subset
subset: pheno_slim
synonym: "dens molaris" EXACT [Wikipedia:Molar_(tooth)]
